The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel approach using neural networks, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
